tiles.name: Markdown
tiles.markdown:
## True Journeys per second
Limitations:
Dynatrace dashboards have a granularity of 1 minute despite the data being recorded at a higher granularity so the graphs aggregate the data to a minute then divide by 60 to get a journeys/second.

**To calculate journey/second metrics using cloudWatch, see our team manual page: [here](https://team-manual.account.gov.uk/teams/IPV-Core-team/Supporting-IPV-Core/using-support-tools/).**
